## Items [/list/:lid/item]

+ Parameters
    + lid (required, integer) - List ID

### Get All Items in List [GET]

This route can return 404 when the list does not exist.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

        [
            {
                "id": 1,
                "listID": 0,
                "name": "Chocolate Milk"
                "quantity": 1,
                "created": "2009-11-10 23:00:00 +0000 UTC m=+0.000000001",
